Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to 123 Meditation App. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our App.
2. Information We Collect
We collect the following personal information when you use our app:
• Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including device ID, type, operating system, and other technical details.
• Name: To personalize your experience and address you appropriately.
• Email Address: To communicate with you, send you updates, and respond to your inquiries.
• Password: To secure your account and ensure that only you can access it.
• Gender: To tailor our content and services to better meet your needs.
3. How We Use Your Information
The information collected from your device will be used to:
• Operate and optimise our app.
• Monitor and analyse app usage and performance.
• Communicate with you regarding updates, features, or issues.
• Enforce our Terms and Conditions and comply with legal obligations.
• Personalizing your experience within the App.
We use the collected information for the following purposes:
• Personalization: To customize your experience within the App based on your preferences and profile information.
• Communication: To send you updates, notifications, and other relevant information about the App.
• Account Management: To manage your account and provide customer support.
4. Data Storage and Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Your data is stored securely and is accessible only by authorized personnel.
5. Data Sharing
We do not sell or rent your device information to third parties. We may share your device information with:
• Service providers who assist us in operating and improving our app.
• Law enforcement or regulatory authorities if required by law or to protect our rights.
We do not share, sell, or disclose your personal information to any third parties, other apps, or users. Your information remains confidential and is used solely for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy.
6. Data Retention
We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including for legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. If you wish to have your data deleted, please contact us using the details provided in the “Contact Us” section below.
7. Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights or if you have any questions about how your data is handled, please contact us as described in the “Contact Us” section below.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy on our App.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
• Email: operations@wyndtechnologies.com
• Address: WYND Technologies Private Limited,#372,3rd Floor Cabin No 305,6th Cross ,Golden Square Wilson Garden, Banglore 560027
10. Acceptance of This Privacy Policy
By using our App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our practices, please do not use the App.
